moveTo(Node) - Method in class gui.DiverSprite
Tell the diver to move from its current location to node dst.
After making move, calling thread will block until the move completes on GUI.
Precondition: dst must be adjacent to the current location and not currently moving.
moveTo(Node) - Method in class gui.GUI
Move the diver on the GUI to destination dest.
Note : This blocks until the diver has moved.
Precondition: dest is adjacent to the diver's current location
